&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;REFUND AND CANCELLATION POLICY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Last Updated: 12 Feb 2026&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;At Robinfood, we take pride in the quality of our products. As a premium health-focused brand by Arrikar Foods, we ensure that every packet leaves our facility in perfect condition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;However, we understand that issues can sometimes occur during transit. This Refund and Cancellation Policy outlines your rights and our procedures for such events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;1. Cancellation Policy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Before Shipment: You may cancel your order if it has not yet been dispatched from our warehouse. To cancel, please email us immediately at info@robinfoodsindia.com or call our customer care number. If the order is cancelled before shipment, a full refund will be initiated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;After Shipment: Once the order has been dispatched/shipped, it cannot be cancelled.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;2. Return Policy (Damaged or Defective Goods)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Due to the perishable nature of food products, we do not accept returns for &quot;change of mind&quot; or personal preference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;We only accept returns or replacements under the following specific conditions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Damaged Product: The package was open, torn, or crushed upon delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Wrong Item: You received a different product than what you ordered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Expired/Spoiled: The product received is past its expiry date or appears spoiled.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;How to Report an Issue: You must notify us within 48 hours of receiving the delivery. Please send an email to info@robinfoodsindia.com with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Your Order ID.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Clear photos/videos of the damaged or wrong product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;A brief description of the issue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Note: We reserve the right to reject return claims if the issue is not reported within 48 hours of delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;3. Refund Policy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Once your return/cancellation request is received and inspected:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Approval: We will notify you via email regarding the approval or rejection of your refund.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Processing: If approved, your refund will be processed immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Timeline: The credit will automatically be applied to your original method of payment (Credit Card, Debit Card, UPI, or Net Banking) within 5 to 7 business days, depending on your bank&#039;s processing time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;4. Late or Missing Refunds&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;If you haven&amp;rsquo;t received a refund within 7-10 days:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;First, check your bank account again.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Contact your credit card company or bank; it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;If you have done all of this and still have not received your refund, please contact us at info@robinfoodsindia.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;5. Contact Information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;For any questions regarding refunds or cancellations, please contact us:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Brand: Robinfood (Arrikar Foods)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Email: info@robinfoodsindia.com&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Website: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.robinfoodsindia.com&quot;&gt;www.robinfoodsindia.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Registered Address: [Insert Full Physical Address Here]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Phone: [Insert Phone Number Here]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
